description: The year is 1942, and hot, young American soldiers are risking life and limb to fight against the threat of Nazi invasion. But when a sadistic German officer Rob Yaeger captures hot, angry private Ty Roderick, a different kind of power struggle begins. Watch gorgeous but deranged POW Tommy Defendi turn on his own young comrade Ludo Sander while cute blonde Private Wilde is made to give up classified information - or else.
title: Prisoner Of War Scene 1
